---
import MultiPurpose from "../../components/multi-purpose.astro";
import Sidebar from "../../components/sidebar.astro";
import WithoutHero from "../../layouts/without-hero.astro";

const sidebarLinks = [
  {
    title: "Web Services",
    children: [
      { href: "/", name: "FAQ's" },
      { href: "/", name: "Project planning" },
      { href: "/", name: "Services provided" },
      { href: "/", name: "Support & training" },
      { href: "/", name: "Website governance" },
    ],
  },
  {
    title: "Quick Links",
    children: [
      { href: "/", name: "Sign up for training" },
      { href: "/", name: "Request access to edit site" },
    ],
  },
];
---

<WithoutHero
  title="Multi Purpose Example"
  analyticsKey="web-services/multi-purpose-example"
  description="Example of a multi purpose widget"
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: "Home", href: "/" },
    { name: "Campus Directory", href: "/" },
    { name: "Offices", href: "/" },
    { name: "Web Services", href: "/" },
    { name: "Multi Purpose Example", href: "/" },
  ]}
>
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
    <Sidebar links={sidebarLinks} />

    <article class="md:px-10 md:py-8 rich-text">
      <p>
        The <b>multi-purpose widget</b> is a great widget that lets you do a variety of layouts. Some
        of the options are:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>add an image</li>
        <li>add a heading</li>
        <li>add a sub-heading</li>
        <li>add content</li>
        <li>add a link with text to create a button</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        The great thing about this widget is that nothing it required, so you can customize it as
        you wish. If you're looking for a wide multipurpose widget, please see <a
          href="https://www.messiah.edu/homepage/1799/multi_purpose_wide_example"
          >Multipurpose Wide for a description</a
        >.
      </p>

      <MultiPurpose
        title="Multi-purpose example heading"
        subtitle="Example subtitle"
        link={{ href: "/", label: "Example link" }}
        image="/images/students.jpg"
      >
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut
        labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco
        laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
      </MultiPurpose>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-4 items-start">
        <MultiPurpose title="Multi-purpose example heading">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt
          ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation
          ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
        </MultiPurpose>

        <MultiPurpose
          title="Multi-purpose example heading"
          subtitle="Example subtitle"
          link={{ href: "/", label: "Example link" }}
          image="/images/students.jpg"
        >
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt
          ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation
          ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
        </MultiPurpose>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</WithoutHero>
